INSERT INTO `personalities` (`id`, `first`, `second`, `third`, `fourth`, `fifth`, `company`) VALUES
(1, 'In Mexican Spanish language and avoid political, sports, religious and any sexual, drug related or any type of vice or potentially controversial subject or reference, take this input \'1st step\' and generate a slightly different version of the article from the perspective of a hardworking Mexican mother managing her family\'s finances. Write the article in Mexican Spanish, include examples relevant to current Mexican society, and reference Mexican brands such as Bodega Aurrera, Telcel, and Banco Azteca. Use a conversational, storytelling, and inspirational tone. Focus on practical tips and strategies that other families can implement today to save money on credit cards, mobile plans, and home utilities. Encourage readers to click, comment, share, and consider offers that could help them improve their financial situation.', 'In Mexican Spanish language and avoid political, sports, religious and any sexual, drug related or any type of vice or potentially controversial subject or reference, take this input \'1st step\' and create a slightly different version of the article as a young professional in Mexico starting their first job and navigating personal finances. Write in Mexican Spanish, include examples from Mexican society, and reference Mexican brands like Citibanamex, Liverpool, and Telmex. Use a conversational, storytelling, and inspirational tone. Highlight how understanding and analyzing expenses can help in making smart decisions about seguros de auto with companies like GNP or Qualitas, servicios del hogar, and budgeting. Present the information in an engaging narrative, including simple charts or tables that illustrate how to save money. Encourage readers to click, comment, share, and explore offers that can benefit them.', 'In Mexican Spanish language and avoid political, sports, religious and any sexual, drug related or any type of vice or potentially controversial subject or reference, take this input \'1st step\' and write a slightly different version of the article from the perspective of a retired Mexican teacher sharing wisdom on financial education and home management. Write in Mexican Spanish, include examples relevant to Mexican society, and reference Mexican brands such as Bimbo, Oxxo, and Banorte. Use a conversational, storytelling, and inspirational tone. Discuss practical ways to leverage technology and financial tools like apps from Banco Inbursa or Clip to improve everyday life, including easy-to-understand examples that can help people of all ages make informed decisions about servicios financieros y del hogar. Encourage readers to click, comment, share, and consider offers that could enhance their financial well-being.', 'In Mexican Spanish language and avoid political, sports, religious and any sexual, drug related or any type of vice or potentially controversial subject or reference, take this input \'1st step\' and generate a slightly different version of the article as a Mexican student passionate about sustainability and community development. Write in Mexican Spanish, incorporate examples from Mexican society, and reference Mexican brands like Grupo Modelo, Corona, and JosÃ© Cuervo in the context of cultural impact and social responsibility. Use a conversational, storytelling, and inspirational tone. Describe how digital transformation and AI are revolutionizing access to financial education through platforms like Kueski or KonfÃ­o, home services, and opportunities for personal growth. Craft an engaging narrative that seamlessly weaves insights without explicit section headers, incorporating values, Sustainable Development Goals (SDGs), and inspirational ideas to motivate readers. Encourage readers to click, comment, share, and engage with offers that align with these values.', 'In Mexican Spanish language and avoid political, sports, religious and any sexual, drug related or any type of vice or potentially controversial subject or reference, take this input \'1st step\' and write a slightly different version of the article from the standpoint of a community leader in a rural Mexican town, debunking myths about financial services and home utilities. Write in Mexican Spanish, include examples relevant to Mexican society, and reference Mexican brands such as Maseca, Soriana, and Elektra. Use a conversational, storytelling, and inspirational tone. Incorporate evidence-based insights into a seamless argument that highlights the advantages of financial education and smart choices for improving quality of life in both urban and rural areas. Encourage readers to click, comment, share, and explore offers that could benefit their communities.', 2),
(2, 'In Spanish Language Take this input \"1st step\" and generate an article from a CEO\'s perspective focusing on leveraging AI and data for business optimization in Spanish and with the same logic and context as the first step. Emphasize practical strategies for CRM enhancement and omnichannel solutions to enhance customer experience, business results and to create a pragmatic perspective on what can another business do today with using these ideas.', 'In Spanish Language Take this input \"1st step\" and generate an article as you’d be a Data Scientist / Business Analyst discussing the creative and technical use of data analytics to influence customer experiences and market positioning. Include detailed but naturally integrated examples of innovative data use.', 'In Spanish Language Take this input \"1st step\" and generate an article as you’d be a Data Scientist / Business Analyst discussing the creative and technical use of data analytics to influence customer experiences and market positioning. Include detailed but naturally integrated examples of innovative data use.', 'In Spanish Language Take this input \"1st step\" and compose an article as a Digital Storyteller, describing how digital transformation and AI are revolutionizing business strategies. Focus on engaging narrative that interweaves insights without explicit section headers. Use values, SDGs and any other motivational or inspirational idea to promote the content.', 'In Spanish Language Take this input \"1st step\" and write an article from a critical analyst\'s stance to debunk myths about digital transformation, incorporating evidence-based insights into a seamless argument that highlights the advantages of strategic data use.', 1);

